  "source_notes": "Sy Scholfield quotes her on Twitter X: \"A história do meu nascimento: Nasci dia 31/12, porém meia noite, então seria, na verdade, 01/01. Porém registrou-se 12hs em vez de 00hs na certidão, então nasci dia 31/12, 12hs. Portanto, sou e não sou a primeira criança de 1990.\" (Translation: The story of my birth: I was born on 31/12, but at midnight, so it would actually be 01/01. However, 12:00 was registered instead of 00:00 on the birth certificate, so I was born on 31/12, 12:00. So I am and I am not the first child of 1990) [https://x.com/JacyCarvalho/status/1206227781723545600], \"eu não nasci no rio de janeiro pra passar frio\" (I wasn't born in Rio de Janeiro to be cold) [https://x.com/JacyCarvalho/status/1527617828727160835].\\n",
